ve' as answer)","transliteration":"alam","root":"","lemmaId":31},{"id":"71:15:2","ayahNum":15,"wordNum":2,"word":"تَرَوْا۟","meaning":"you (all) see (question with أَلَمْ)","transliteration":"taraw","root":"رأي","lemmaId":null},{"id":"71:15:3","ayahNum":15,"wordNum":3,"word":"كَيْفَ","meaning":"how (asking about manner)","transliteration":"kayfa","root":"كيف","lemmaId":null},{"id":"71:15:4","ayahNum":15,"wordNum":4,"word":"خَلَقَ","meaning":"he created (subject of سَبْعَ سَمٰوٰتٍ)","transliteration":"khalaqa","root":"خلق","lemmaId":null},{"id":"71:15:5","ayahNum":15,"wordNum":5,"word":"ٱللَّهُ","meaning":"Allah (the one true God who created seven heavens)","transliteration":"l-lahu","root":"أله","lemmaId":490},{"id":"71:15:6","ayahNum":15,"wordNum":6,"word":"سَبْعَ","meaning":"seven (object of خَلَقَ/created)","transliteration":"sabʿa","root":"سبع","lemmaId":1968},{"id":"71:15:7","ayahNum":15,"wordNum":7,"word":"سَمٰوٰتٍ","meaning":"heavens/skies (as object)","transliteration":"samāwātin","root":"سمو","lemmaId":null},{"id":"71:15:8","ayahNum":15,"wordNum":8,"word":"طِبَاقًا","meaning":"in layers (describing how سَمٰوٰتٍ/heavens are arranged)","transliteration":"ṭibāqan","root":"طبق","lemmaId":null},{"id":"71:16:1","ayahNum":16,"wordNum":1,"word":"وَجَعَلَ","meaning":"and he made (something into something else)","transliteration":"wajaʿala","root":"جعل","lemmaId":null},{"id":"71:16:2","ayahNum":16,"wordNum":2,"word":"ٱلْقَمَرَ","meaning":"the moon (object of جَعَلَ - He made)","transliteration":"l-qamara","root":"قمر","lemmaId":null},{"id":"71:16:3","ayahNum":16,"wordNum":3,"word":"فِيهِنَّ","meaning":"in them (referring to the seven heavens)","transliteration":"fīhinna","root":"","lemmaId":2887},{"id":"71:16:4","ayahNum":16,"wordNum":4,"word":"نُورًا","meaning":"a light (object of جَعَلَ - He made)","transliteration":"nūran","root":"نور","lemmaId":4109},{"id":"71:16:5","ayahNum":16,"wordNum":5,"word":"وَجَعَلَ","meaning":"and He made/put (referring to Allah's creation of الْقَمَرَ - the moon)","transliteration":"wajaʿala","root":"جعل","lemmaId":1223},{"id":"71:16:6","ayahNum":16,"wordNum":6,"word":"ٱلشَّمْسَ","meaning":"the sun (object of جَعَلَ/made)","transliteration":"l-shamsa","root":"شمس","lemmaId":2176},{"id":"71:16:7","ayahNum":16,"wordNum":7,"word":"سِرَاجًا","meaning":"a lamp (object of جَعَلَ/made)","transliteration":"sirājan","root":"سرج","lemmaId":null},{"id":"71:17:1","ayahNum":17,"wordNum":1,"word":"وَٱللَّهُ","meaning":"And Allah (as the doer of أَنۢبَتَكُم - grew you)","transliteration":"wal-lahu","root":"","lemmaId":650},{"id":"71:17:2","ayahNum":17,"wordNum":2,"word":"أَنۢبَتَكُم","meaning":"He caused you all to grow (Allah caused you to grow from الْأَرْضِ)","transliteration":"anbatakum","root":"نبت","lemmaId":null},{"id":"71:17:3","ayahNum":17,"wordNum":3,"word":"مِّنَ","meaning":"from the","transliteration":"mina","root":"","lemmaId":3464},{"id":"71:17:4","ayahNum":17,"wordNum":4,"word":"ٱلْأَرْضِ","meaning":"from the earth (after مِنَ)","transliteration":"l-arḍi","root":"أرض","lemmaId":null},{"id":"71:17:5","ayahNum":17,"wordNum":5,"word":"نَبَاتًا","meaning":"as a growth (object of أَنۢبَتَ)","transliteration":"nabātan","root":"نبت","lemmaId":null},{"id":"71:18:1","ayahNum":18,"wordNum":1,"word":"ثُمَّ","meaning":"then (connects to يُعِيدُكُمْ - He will return you)","transliteration":"thumma","root":"","lemmaId":1171},{"id":"71:18:2","ayahNum":18,"wordNum":2,"word":"يُعِيدُكُمْ","meaning":"he will return you all (into the earth)","transliteration":"yuʿīdukum","root":"عود","lemmaId":null},{"id":"71:18:3","ayahNum":18,"wordNum":3,"word":"فِيهَا","meaning":"in it/her (referring to الأَرْضِ 'the earth' which is feminine)","transliteration":"fīhā","root":"","lemmaId":2887},{"id":"71:18:4","ayahNum":18,"wordNum":4,"word":"وَيُخْرِجُكُمْ","meaning":"and he makes you all come out","transliteration":"wayukh'rijukum","root":"خرج","lemmaId":1523},{"id":"71:18:5","ayahNum":18,"wordNum":5,"word":"إِخْرَاجًا","meaning":"a bringing out (object of يُخْرِجُكُمْ - He brings you out)","transliteration":"ikh'rājan","root":"خرج","lemmaId":1523},{"id":"71:19:1","ayahNum":19,"wordNum":1,"word":"وَٱللَّهُ","meaning":"And Allah (as the subject of جَعَلَ)","transliteration":"wal-lahu","root":"","lemmaId":650},{"id":"71:19:2","ayahNum":19,"wordNum":2,"word":"جَعَلَ","meaning":"he made (connected to لَكُمُ ٱلْأَرْضَ - for you the earth)","transliteration":"jaʿala","root":"جعل","lemmaId":null},{"id":"71:19:3","ayahNum":19,"wordNum":3,"word":"لَكُمُ","meaning":"for you all (connects لَكُمُ to جَعَلَ)","transliteration":"lakumu","root":"","lemmaId":3146},{"id":"71:19:4","ayahNum":19,"wordNum":4,"word":"ٱلْأَرْضَ","meaning":"the earth (as the object that Allah made)","transliteration":"l-arḍa","root":"أرض","lemmaId":null},{"id":"71:19:5","ayahNum":19,"wordNum":5,"word":"بِسَاطًا","meaning":"a carpet/mat (object of جَعَلَ)","transliteration":"bisāṭan","root":"بسط","lemmaId":null},{"id":"71:20:1","ayahNum":20,"wordNum":1,"word":"لِّتَسْلُكُوا۟","meaning":"so that you all may follow a path (from مِنْهَا)","transliteration":"litaslukū","root":"سلك","lemmaId":null},{"id":"71:20:2","ayahNum":20,"wordNum":2,"word":"مِنْهَا","meaning":"from it/her (referring to Earth)","transliteration":"min'hā","root":"","lemmaId":3464},{"id":"71:20:3","ayahNum":20,"wordNum":3,"word":"سُبُلًا","meaning":"paths (object of لِتَسْلُكُوا - for you to travel upon)","transliteration":"subulan","root":"سبل","lemmaId":null},{"id":"71:20:4","ayahNum":20,"wordNum":4,"word":"فِجَاجًا","meaning":"wide paths (describing سُبُلًا/roads)","transliteration":"fijājan","root":"فجج","lemmaId":null},{"id":"71:21:1","ayahNum":21,"wordNum":1,"word":"قَالَ","meaning":"he said","transliteration":"qāla","root":"قول","lemmaId":null},{"id":"71:21:2","ayahNum":21,"wordNum":2,"word":"نُوحٌ","meaning":"Noah (as an independent subject)","transliteration":"nūḥun","root":"","lemmaId":4108},{"id":"71:21:3","ayahNum":21,"wordNum":3,"word":"رَّبِّ","meanin